To complete setup:
1. Create these files in root:
   - `CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md`
   - `CONTRIBUTING.md`
   - `SECURITY.md`

2. Add this GitHub Actions workflow (`.github/workflows/ci_cd/build_pipeline.yml`):
```yaml
name: VidAGI CI/CD Pipeline

on:
  push:
    branches: [main]
  pull_request:
    branches: [main]

jobs:
  build-and-test:
    runs-on: windows-latest
    steps:
    - name: Checkout code
      uses: actions/checkout@v3

    - name: Setup .NET
      uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v2
      with:
        dotnet-version: 6.0.x

    - name: Restore dependencies
      run: dotnet restore ./src/VIDAGI.sln

    - name: Build solution
      run: dotnet build ./src/VIDAGI.sln --configuration Release --no-restore

    - name: Run tests
      run: |
        dotnet test ./tests/unit_tests/UnitTests.csproj --configuration Release --no-build
        dotnet test ./tests/integration_tests/IntegrationTests.csproj --configuration Release --no-build 
